people_also_ask.question: Is Ms Pac-Man Pac-Man's Wife?
people_also_ask.heading: Pac-Man (ミズ・パックマン Mizu Pakkuman), also known as Pepper in the animated series or Pac-Girl (パックガール Pakkugāru) prior to her relationship with Pac-Man, is the deuteragonist of the Pac-Man series. She is Pac-Man's wife and sidekick, and is the mother of Jr. Pac-Man and Baby Pac-Man.
